::Prowl/Striker::

Prowl's eyes widen and his mechfluid flow speeds up at Iron Raptor's comment. 
He knew she was only kidding, but the effect the coment had on the maximal 
was amazing.

He looks at Iron Raptor and grins. "Is that an order, 'commander'?" he says 
rather mockingly.

Striker walks up to them, trying not to break out laughing, "Allright, just 
get repaired. I don't wanna know," he says, walking off toward the Ark.
